 Help Those in Need, Be Tolerant, Resist Fear, Organise and Let's Get 'em from Below. *(16:49:00)** RT @junayed_: .@Nigel_Farage http://t.co/DYrdXVWuSb *(16:51:00)** RT @markthomasinfo: Ah Well, It's not Called the Struggle for Nothing. Come On. *(16:52:00)** RT @KermodeMovie: Oh Well. Still, All together now:\"Arise Ye Starvelings from Your Slumbers, Arise Ye Prisoners of want ...\" *(16:52:00)** RT @sparkydeathcap: One saving Grace is that Vast Majority of the Electorate Didn't want a Tory Govt. Which Will Keep Us All Warm when We're Sleeping in a Park. *(16:53:00)** RT @wasabihann: UK, You've Allowed a Man Who once Set Fire to a £50 Note in front of a Homeless Man Become Your Prime Minister TWICE. I Can't. #GE02015 *(16:53:00)** RT @RoseUnwin: A Bad Day if You're Poor, Disabled, Studying, Young, an Immigrant, Working in the Public Sector, a Child. A Perfect Day if You're Rich. *(16:53:00)** RT @davidwearing: Are You a \"shy Tory\"? That Thing Embarrassing You is Your Conscience. You're Supposed to Listen to It. *(16:53:00)** RT @davegray: Do Yourself a favor and Subscribe to @austinkleon 's Newsletter. It's F---ing Awesome. http://t.co/fPW0WxP713 *(16:54:00)** RT @wolfwhistle: The UK Will Be Absolutely Fine. As long as You're not Sick or Old or Unemployed or Disabled or an Immigrant or Need an Education. #GE2015 *(16:54:00)** RT @ssx: Hey, #usa, Can You come and Invade the #uk? Our Democracy is Fucked, Oh and We Have Some Oil. #ge2015 (cc @BarackObama) *(07:59:00)** https://t.co/vChcPuw0JQ":[13,16],"#Lifestream Entries<a name=\"giftttdy\"></a>##### Fitbit Statistics* Daily Activity Summary - *Total steps:* 16678, *Floors climbed:* , *Calories burned:* 3495, *Elevation gained:* Meters, *Traveled:* 13.34 Kilometers, *Sedentary minutes:* 456, *Lightly Active minutes:* 557, *Fairly Active minutes:* 20, *Very Active minutes:* 0 *(23:59:00)*<a name=\"giftttdy\"></a>##### Tweets* Mixed Feelings. 5 More Fucking Years of Tories Screwing Us Over, but @GYJARMY and @SpudTayl